alue":{"title":"规范描述","id":"规范描述","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#dom-context-2d-font-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.font"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.font","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/font/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko-specific_注解","title":"Gecko-specific 注解","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>基于 Gecko 的浏览器，例如 Firefox，实现了一个非标准的并且不赞成使用的属性 <code>ctx.mozTextStyle</code> 。不要使用此属性。</li>\n  <li>在 Gecko 中，当将系统字体设置为 canvas 2D 上下文的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/font\" title=\"font\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>font</code></a>（例如菜单）的值时，获取用于无法返回期望字体的字体值（不返回任何内容）。这已在 Firefox 57（<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1374885\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;1374885</a>）中发布的 Firefox 的<a href=\"https://wiki.mozilla.org/Quantum/Stylo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Quantum/Stylo</a>并行 CSS 引擎中修复。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>接口定义，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范描述","id":"规范描述"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.font 是 Canvas 2D API 描述绘制文字时，当前字体样式的属性。使用和 CSS font 规范相同的字符串值。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.font","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.font","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.font","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.font","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/canvasrende